text.section:
A court crier shall receive the per diem compensation provided by this section for attending the circuit court:
Caroline -- $15;
Cecil -- As set by the County Commissioners;
Kent -- $17.50;
Queen Anne's -- As set by the court and approved by the county government;
Somerset -- As set by the County Commissioners;
Talbot -- As set by the County Commissioners;
Wicomico -- As set by the County Commissioners.
